Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.05,0:00:08.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(330,400)\fad(1000,000)}聖天空戰記
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.43,0:00:12.43,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是只要墜入愛河每個人都會變得如此孤單?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.51,0:00:21.42,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是正擁抱著比黑暗要更深沉的苦楚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.48,0:00:34.56,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一切必定都是為了讓我倆能綻放光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.03,0:00:39.47,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我愛著你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.53,0:00:43.97,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直用心凝視著你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.04,0:00:48.48,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信著你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.54,0:00:53.04,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便是在寒冷的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.07,0:01:15.50,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在用淚水來呼喚你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.57,0:01:20.03,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不需要約定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.11,0:01:28.91,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你早就給了我 最寶貴的堅強
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.43,0:00:12.43,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ねえ 愛したら誰もが こんな孤独になるの
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.51,0:00:21.42,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ねえ 暗闇よりも深い苦しみ 抱きしめてるの
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.48,0:00:34.56,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何もかもが二人 輝くためきっと
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.03,0:00:39.47,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君を君を愛してる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.53,0:00:43.97,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心で見つめている
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.04,0:00:48.48,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君を君を信じてる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.54,0:00:53.04,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寒い夜も
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.07,0:01:15.50,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涙で今呼びかける
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.57,0:01:20.03,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約束などいらない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.11,0:01:28.91,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君がくれた大切な強さだから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.52,0:01:35.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼要那麼久
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.36,0:01:38.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心,老大的命很硬
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.16,0:01:40.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對死不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.96,0:01:41.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說得也對
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.73,0:01:44.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞連
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.57,0:01:50.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,治療順利完畢了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.11,0:01:52.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞連他沒事了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.94,0:01:53.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.91,0:01:56.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在雖然因為麻醉,還沒醒過來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.91,0:01:57.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜拉娜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.55,0:02:08.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藍瞳的王子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.56,0:02:12.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是幸好有蜜拉娜公主在
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.89,0:02:16.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有公主在的話,要進入弗雷特就簡單多了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.43,0:02:17.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.60,0:02:22.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜拉娜公主的姊姊\N瑪蓮妮公主就是嫁到弗雷特去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.90,0:02:24.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪蓮妮公主？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.34,0:02:25.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.44,0:02:27.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是阿斯多利亞的長公主
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.31,0:02:30.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於三年前不幸病故
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.95,0:02:33.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,韶下王子一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.35,0:02:36.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗雷特公國的王子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.49,0:02:48.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯多利亞王國三公主
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.30,0:02:52.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯頓·莎拉·蜜拉娜殿下來訪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.77,0:02:54.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長途跋涉辛苦各位了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.74,0:02:59.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗雷特公王正巧外出巡視領土
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.54,0:03:01.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就由我來接待各位
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.41,0:03:03.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西特？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.91,0:03:04.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您是西特王子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.68,0:03:06.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.92,0:03:09.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不見了,蜜拉娜阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.55,0:03:12.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您真的是長大了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.89,0:03:13.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都要認不出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.92,0:03:18.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次見面時,您還好小好小
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.03,0:03:20.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.96,0:03:25.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說這次有亞連·歇薩爾大人隨行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.97,0:03:27.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那一位嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.04,0:03:32.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母后生前常跟我說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.17,0:03:38.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯多利亞有著蓋亞最棒的劍客亞連·歇薩爾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.38,0:03:39.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是位無敵的騎士
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.91,0:03:42.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,駕駛人型裝甲的姿態,十分華麗英勇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.58,0:03:44.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她說總有一天我一定能夠見到他
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.75,0:03:45.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.09,0:03:51.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這位是法尼利亞的國王,梵·法尼爾大人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.56,0:03:55.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.30,0:03:59.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法尼利亞王,我為我的失禮感到抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.03,0:04:02.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗雷特歡迎您的來訪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.60,0:04:06.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請您將這裏當成自己的國家,別感到拘束
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.31,0:04:06.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.28,0:04:10.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於弗雷特公國的情誼,我深表感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.01,0:04:15.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿姨,亞連人呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.52,0:04:17.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經沒有大礙了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.52,0:04:19.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的脈搏也穩定下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.09,0:04:21.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多也該清醒過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.32,0:04:23.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.86,0:04:26.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞連·歇薩爾竟然會被人擊敗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.53,0:04:29.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說得也對
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.47,0:04:33.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能真的有無敵的騎士
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.54,0:04:40.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母后只是在對身為孩童的我,說故事罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.65,0:04:48.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞連
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.88,0:04:50.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老大…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.09,0:04:53.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.09,0:04:57.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜拉娜公主？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.23,0:05:06.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞連,這位是弗雷特公國的西特王子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.83,0:05:07.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞連
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.51,0:05:15.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那只戒指…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.51,0:05:17.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西特…王子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.68,0:05:21.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還好吧,亞連大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.58,0:05:24.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.79,0:05:27.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寨巴哈正打算要攻打這個國家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.56,0:05:31.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請讓在下晉見您父王…晉見公王
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.29,0:05:34.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寨巴哈馬上就會前來侵略了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.53,0:05:36.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞連\N亞連
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.00,0:05:38.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西特王子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.00,0:05:41.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞連他捨棄自己的國家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.77,0:05:44.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不惜讓自己蒙受污名,就是為了要傳達此事而來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.21,0:05:47.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您的母后所言非假
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.88,0:05:49.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他才是真正的騎士
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.35,0:05:53.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞連
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.95,0:05:56.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我還是難以相信
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.85,0:05:58.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寨巴哈為什麼要…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.95,0:06:02.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要審問我們捉來的寨巴哈兵\N應該就能知道真相了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.36,0:06:05.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這件事我已經安排好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.29,0:06:07.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安排？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.23,0:06:08.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前公王不在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.93,0:06:13.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,審問那名士兵時一定要小心謹慎才行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.20,0:06:17.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍逃到弗雷特去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.47,0:06:18.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.54,0:06:20.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,俘虜也被帶過去了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.98,0:06:22.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用不著擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.24,0:06:24.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米蓋爾可是我的部下耶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.58,0:06:27.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就是死也不會招的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.12,0:06:28.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想也是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.75,0:06:31.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但弗雷特有普拉克度
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.42,0:06:33.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.99,0:06:35.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普拉克度
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.89,0:06:39.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指的是擅長行使催眠術的僧侶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.19,0:06:41.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若是中了催眠術
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.70,0:06:44.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概連內心深處的情報,都會被挖出來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.43,0:06:48.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已收到消息得知,他正前往戈達西姆
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.24,0:06:50.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.81,0:06:52.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得在他抵達前滅□才行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.84,0:06:54.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然作戰計劃會曝光的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.68,0:06:56.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宗基啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.35,0:06:58.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.81,0:07:01.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什麼人？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.75,0:07:04.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這股臭味是怎麼回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.92,0:07:09.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是幻人嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.69,0:07:13.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宗基,我有事要你去辦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.80,0:07:14.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.03,0:07:18.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小的生命都奉獻給弗肯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.04,0:07:22.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.47,0:07:25.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜拉娜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.04,0:07:28.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你忘了這個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.18,0:07:31.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的包包
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.05,0:07:35.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你,蜜拉娜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.42,0:07:39.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼會曉得我在這裏？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.85,0:07:40.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.62,0:07:44.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直有種感覺,我們會再見面
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.90,0:07:49.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來得共處一段時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.93,0:07:52.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們好好相處吧,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.84,0:07:58.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女人的直覺,是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.24,0:08:01.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那艘船嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.68,0:08:04.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種船艦一發炮彈就可以打下來了說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.38,0:08:06.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪蘭度大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.11,0:08:08.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就麻煩您了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.85,0:08:09.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.20,0:08:23.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然會用上幻人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.25,0:08:41.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的品味還真差啊,弗肯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.59,0:08:46.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真叫人拿您沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.36,0:08:48.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到您還是跟了過來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.52,0:08:51.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真正的想法我懂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.96,0:08:56.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你之所以會離開國家,並不全是為了弗雷特吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.90,0:09:02.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是憂心阿斯多利亞,遲早也會被寨巴哈毀滅
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.31,0:09:06.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總有一天父王會明瞭的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.78,0:09:10.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你比任何人都還要關心阿斯多利亞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.12,0:09:19.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是怎麼了啊,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.82,0:09:21.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼早就把我叫出來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.76,0:09:25.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅露露,為什麼連你也一起跟過來了啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.13,0:09:29.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不放心讓梵大人和你獨處
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.40,0:09:30.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.73,0:09:34.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你總是能準確地說出隱形人型裝甲的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.74,0:09:35.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.64,0:09:38.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若要與他們正面抗衡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.44,0:09:41.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我需要你的幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.41,0:09:43.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.84,0:09:45.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎樣才能找出隱形敵人的所在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.78,0:09:47.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.66,0:09:56.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是刺客嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.29,0:10:01.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然有本事在不被我發現的情況下潛進來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.13,0:10:03.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.56,0:10:32.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.76,0:10:34.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好的身體
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.71,0:10:52.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是一心想著自己想找的東西罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.95,0:10:54.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦感覺到我想找的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.92,0:10:56.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,墜子就會朝它的所在方位擺動
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.95,0:10:58.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等到習慣之後
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.05,0:11:01.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至還可以直接在腦海中想像墜子的存在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.39,0:11:03.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們要找什麼好呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.33,0:11:05.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想想…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.86,0:11:07.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵大人,找我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.50,0:11:09.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就請您找我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.63,0:11:14.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.71,0:11:19.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們在做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.14,0:11:21.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不曉得
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.18,0:11:25.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵大人一定能夠找到我的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.75,0:11:29.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要在腦海裏想著她的模樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.19,0:11:32.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沉淀思緒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.09,0:11:34.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,專心一意地想
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.62,0:11:36.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要盡可能清晰地想著
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.59,0:11:39.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢慢來不要緊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.59,0:11:42.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到她的模樣浮現為止
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.80,0:11:44.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯,她有條尾巴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.23,0:11:46.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耳朵尖尖的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.13,0:11:48.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頭髮卷卷的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.17,0:11:50.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大大的圓眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.50,0:11:52.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,個性不太可愛,嘴巴又很惡劣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.74,0:11:55.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下我一定要拿她的腳來磨爪子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.58,0:11:57.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.01,0:11:58.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我學不會
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.41,0:12:00.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能就這樣放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.58,0:12:03.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許沒辦法馬上學會
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.78,0:12:05.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但習慣了之後,誰都辦得到的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.45,0:12:07.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.40,0:12:24.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那裏
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.54,0:12:27.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不要出去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.68,0:12:28.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅露露？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.74,0:12:32.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在,梵大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.48,0:12:36.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西特王子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.68,0:12:38.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了不起,真是了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.52,0:12:39.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是怎麼辦到的,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.02,0:12:40.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會知道呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.22,0:12:42.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.99,0:12:44.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西特王子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.36,0:12:46.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您用不著理會這種傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.66,0:12:49.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她只是個算命女罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.16,0:12:51.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老是猜中自己跟他人的過去及未來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.80,0:12:53.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺真的很不好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.90,0:12:55.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是抱歉喔\N真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.97,0:12:59.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的有辦法預知未來嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.81,0:13:01.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼說好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.04,0:13:04.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在占卜的時候會無意間得知
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.98,0:13:06.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.71,0:13:09.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就連普拉克度也沒辦法算出未來的說
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.85,0:13:14.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳,下次可以請你幫我算算未來嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.62,0:13:16.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.82,0:13:18.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.86,0:13:21.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的,王子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.66,0:13:24.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波利斯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.70,0:13:29.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才接獲消息說普拉克度大人已經抵達港□了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.17,0:13:31.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.14,0:13:32.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王子,我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.04,0:13:37.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次的任務麻煩你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.15,0:13:39.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還勞你多多費心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.11,0:13:41.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請交給我處理
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.92,0:13:44.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波利斯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.35,0:13:48.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望能與那名俘虜獨處
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.99,0:13:50.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.97,0:14:02.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是米蓋爾,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.74,0:14:04.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼會知道我的名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.01,0:14:08.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是弗肯大人派來的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.05,0:14:12.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞連,該用餐了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.95,0:14:15.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要多吃點,早日康復吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.12,0:14:16.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜拉娜公主
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.32,0:14:17.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.65,0:14:20.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以請您幫我找小瞳過來嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.86,0:14:24.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可思議的女人？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.46,0:14:25.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.83,0:14:29.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她明確地指出了,我那理應\N不會被看見的人型裝甲位置
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.90,0:14:33.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曉得了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.27,0:14:36.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她就交給我對付吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.90,0:14:38.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你先把我放出去！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.94,0:14:39.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.51,0:14:43.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你得為我做一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.02,0:14:51.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波利斯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.72,0:14:55.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是怎麼了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.19,0:14:56.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經完成準備了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.39,0:14:59.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普拉克度大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.73,0:15:00.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西特王子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.40,0:15:03.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也請讓我在一旁觀看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.57,0:15:06.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他已經進入催眠狀態了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.20,0:15:08.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請發問吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.47,0:15:10.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.94,0:15:13.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寨巴哈兵,你叫什麼名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.91,0:15:15.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米蓋爾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.58,0:15:17.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米蓋爾·拉巴利耶爾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.45,0:15:20.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在我國國境做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.68,0:15:23.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是受阿斯多利亞所托
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.75,0:15:25.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追捕叛國者
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.05,0:15:26.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叛國者？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.22,0:15:28.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你指的是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.92,0:15:32.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是刻意利用法尼利亞王之名
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.83,0:15:34.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打算奪取王位的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.33,0:15:36.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞連·歇薩爾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.83,0:15:39.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞…亞連他？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.57,0:15:42.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.57,0:15:45.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這混帳別胡亂撒謊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.31,0:15:47.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有說謊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.68,0:15:50.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那他又為什麼要將你交給我們？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.58,0:15:54.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他說只要我肯替他說謊他就會釋放我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.68,0:15:55.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說謊？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.68,0:15:59.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欺騙弗雷特使其與阿斯多利亞開戰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.99,0:16:03.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓他能夠趁亂將阿斯多利亞占為已有
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.76,0:16:06.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.49,0:16:07.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.03,0:16:09.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在騙人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.26,0:16:10.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.67,0:16:13.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是騙人的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.87,0:16:15.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我占卜？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.37,0:16:19.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望你能佔卜一下\N那名被俘虜來的寨巴哈兵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.34,0:16:21.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞連,占卜這種事豈能當真…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.34,0:16:22.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.88,0:16:23.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞連
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.61,0:16:25.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緊急動員
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.08,0:16:27.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,派遣近衛軍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.28,0:16:29.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏就交給你們了\N是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.85,0:16:32.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危險
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.19,0:16:34.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紛爭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.56,0:16:36.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一觸即發
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.23,0:16:40.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後是龍的戰士
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.06,0:16:42.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這指的應該是梵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.93,0:16:43.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.16,0:16:44.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.30,0:16:46.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.30,0:16:48.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.94,0:16:53.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某種巨大的力量,將為了使一切重生而引導其步向終結
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.81,0:16:55.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切的終結？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.94,0:16:57.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是寨巴哈的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.28,0:16:59.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後關於那名俘虜…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.65,0:17:01.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,預備的卡片？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.32,0:17:04.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明明都是分開放的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.02,0:17:06.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空白的卡片
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.69,0:17:08.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該不會是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.99,0:17:13.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該還能敔動
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.26,0:17:15.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想要去哪裏？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.30,0:17:16.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波利斯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.80,0:17:19.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.17,0:17:21.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西特王子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.54,0:17:23.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞連
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.87,0:17:25.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到你竟然會是個叛徒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.61,0:17:27.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您怎麼那麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.71,0:17:28.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西特王子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.91,0:17:32.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西特…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.88,0:17:35.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波利斯大人,俘虜逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.92,0:17:36.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.05,0:17:40.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能…跟占卜結果一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.12,0:17:43.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是人型裝甲…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.22,0:17:45.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好,還能動
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.73,0:17:46.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,披風也還能用
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.39,0:17:48.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危險…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.10,0:17:52.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是白費工夫
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.13,0:17:55.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你應該馬上逃走的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.71,0:18:00.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.38,0:18:03.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寨巴哈的人型裝甲！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.39,0:18:15.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,壓力不足嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.33,0:18:19.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.73,0:18:22.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.73,0:18:24.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想得美
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.93,0:18:28.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人…人型裝甲不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.67,0:18:29.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快出動裝甲隊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.74,0:18:33.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在哪裏？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.48,0:18:35.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他逃到哪裏去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.88,0:18:39.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.35,0:18:43.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個女的不在,他就沒辦法看穿隱形披風
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.22,0:18:46.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在哪裏？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.42,0:18:48.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他會從哪裏攻擊過來？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.69,0:18:52.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來試試看好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.90,0:19:03.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他這是想幹嘛？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.97,0:19:05.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無妨
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.41,0:19:07.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要打倒他
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.88,0:19:11.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪蘭度大人一定會,原諒我遭人俘虜的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.78,0:19:18.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,專心地想著要找的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.22,0:19:21.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要專心想就一定能夠看見
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.03,0:19:29.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要將流體金屬集中到單一爪子上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.66,0:19:30.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能夠攻擊得了他
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.73,0:19:32.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪裏？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.70,0:19:35.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寨巴哈的人型裝甲究竟在哪裏？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.47,0:19:41.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後面
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.21,0:19:41.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.95,0:19:51.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為…為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.90,0:20:09.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休想逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.51,0:20:15.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們這是在做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.68,0:20:19.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.92,0:20:24.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我傷成這樣根本無法脫身
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.25,0:20:25.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼辦才好？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.33,0:20:37.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.93,0:20:40.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我可不能讓人給識破
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.67,0:20:45.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠見到隱形物體的力量,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.57,0:20:47.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得去探探虛實才行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.81,0:20:49.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.74,0:20:51.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一定是有什麼誤會
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.41,0:20:52.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要調查就一定能知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.95,0:20:54.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西特王子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.52,0:21:00.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母后總是對我談論你的事跡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.92,0:21:02.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我一直都很尊敬你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.59,0:21:04.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.09,0:21:08.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母后居然是在對我撒謊…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.96,0:21:10.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西特王子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.73,0:21:15.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您曾經打從心底信賴過某個人嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.97,0:21:19.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信他人這件事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.54,0:21:22.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有時會比上戰場還需要更多的勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.71,0:21:24.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西特王子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.68,0:21:28.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您能明白那份勇氣的意義嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.28,0:21:33.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候我感覺到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.65,0:21:35.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞連與西特王子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.89,0:21:39.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們兩人之間存在著某種強烈的羈絆
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.67,0:22:55.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.77,0:22:58.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是你在壞我好事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.44,0:23:02.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們的同伴死了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.08,0:23:06.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死的預言
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.00,0:21:57.07,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月兒彼方藍色探照燈照耀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.61,0:22:05.52,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然降臨的天使 你究竟是誰?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.98,0:22:13.15,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命運的門扉即將開啟　So just fall in love
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.46,0:22:19.30,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕不放過這令人興奮的瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.37,0:22:21.66,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't stop,baby
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.90,0:22:26.67,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那燃燒般的神秘雙眸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.74,0:22:30.51,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天真無邪的笑容讓我傾倒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.58,0:22:34.31,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞳眸深處的暗示只傳遞給你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.38,0:22:38.32,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始了無止盡的旅程
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.38,0:22:41.82,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內心的鼓動無法抑制
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.88,0:22:49.29,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想帶著你一起走
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.00,0:21:57.07,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月の向こう　蒼い Search light　重なる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.61,0:22:05.51,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然舞い降りたAngel　そう　君は誰?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.98,0:22:13.15,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今　運命の　扉が開く　So just fall in love
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.46,0:22:19.29,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸騒ぎするこの瞬間を逃がさない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.36,0:22:21.66,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't stop,baby
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.90,0:22:26.67,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,焼けそうな　君の Mystic eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.74,0:22:30.50,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無邪気な笑顔で　Breaking down
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.57,0:22:34.30,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君だけに　瞳の奥の合図
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.38,0:22:38.31,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果てない　旅は始まる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.38,0:22:41.82,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,もう止まらない　胸の鼓動
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.88,0:22:49.29,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君を　さらっていきたい

